10:T40f,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"Movie","name":"Mom's Friend 2","description":"An art student named Gwang-ho gets dumped by his girlfriend because she was only his source of comfort, and that he's a Mama's boy and a premature ejaculator. He tries to avoid seeing her by going to a different academy and that's when his mother introduces him to her friend Soo-yeon, a sophisticated and intelligent looking woman. Gwang-ho falls for her.  Gwang-ho's mother suddenly leaves for Australia because his father is sick and Gwang-ho gets to stay in Soo-yeon's house for a few days. Looking at her, he thinks of all the things he would like to do with her and Soo-yeon's niece Ha-kyeong stimulates him to do something about his feelings.","image":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/mLlke4cd9R65FYqtMVUZ3h3Z2z9.jpg","datePublished":"2016-09-01","numberOfEpisodes":null,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","inLanguage":"ko","genre":["Romance",null,null,null],"aggregateRating":{"@type":"AggregateRating","ratingValue":6.1,"bestRating":10,"ratingCount":15}}5:[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$10"}}],["$","$L11",null,{"initialDrama":{"id":"523d8348-df3e-4f9a-ae79-9b0323d83d78","tmdb_id":412092,"imdb_id":"tt11772768","content_type":"movie","title":"Mom's Friend 2","original_title":"엄마친구 2","overview":"An art student named Gwang-ho gets dumped by his girlfriend because she was only his source of comfort, and that he's a Mama's boy and a premature ejaculator. He tries to avoid seeing her by going to a different academy and that's when his mother introduces him to her friend Soo-yeon, a sophisticated and intelligent looking woman. Gwang-ho falls for her.  Gwang-ho's mother suddenly leaves for Australia because his father is sick and Gwang-ho gets to stay in Soo-yeon's house for a few days. Looking at her, he thinks of all the things he would like to do with her and Soo-yeon's niece Ha-kyeong stimulates him to do something about his feelings.","poster_path":"/mLlke4cd9R65FYqtMVUZ3h3Z2z9.jpg","backdrop_path":"/dhaHfxS7AVNG53xdHOfJO5hRQbW.jpg","release_date":"2016-09-01","first_air_date":null,"status":"published","original_language":"ko","origin_country":["KR"],"genres":[{"id":10749,"name":"Romance"},"erotic film","romance film","drama film"],"popularity":5.4794,"vote_average":6.1,"vote_count":15,"runtime":92,"number_of_seasons":null,"number_of_episodes":null,"created_at":"2026-01-31T22:02:56.612137+00:00","updated_at":"2026-02-23T13:23:27.148+00:00","tagline":null,"homepage":null,"budget":0,"revenue":0,"production_companies":[],"production_countries":[{"name":"South Korea","iso_3166_1":"KR"}],"spoken_languages":[{"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","english_name":"Korean"}],"networks":[],"last_air_date":null,"in_production":null,"tmdb_status":"Released","content_rating":null,"keywords":[{"id":155477,"name":"softcore"}],"alternative_titles":[],"videos":[],"watch_providers":{"results":{}},"wikidata_id":"Q28699303","tvdb_id":null,"wikipedia_url":null,"overview_source":"tmdb","import_batch_id":null,"import_batch_name":null,"imported_at":"2026-02-07T14:49:53.785279+00:00","region":"KR","main_poster":"/mLlke4cd9R65FYqtMVUZ3h3Z2z9.jpg","images":{"logos":[],"posters":[{"width":2000,"height":3000,"file_path":"/mLlke4cd9R65FYqtMVUZ3h3Z2z9.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","vote_average":3.334},{"width":1200,"height":1800,"file_path":"/e2UHXORYo0e9Zr32k9uYMV239Jd.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0}],"backdrops":[{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/dhaHfxS7AVNG53xdHOfJO5hRQbW.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":3.334},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/yOQQjno6Bvfgefp21MapDfTcq9J.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/bAcHGbdn5HrlRGnhCGSVHzD6hmo.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/8I2FA1r9JeC7Y9zzQcSUjXhxdrG.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0}]},"enriched_at":"2026-04-21T03:32:26.866+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"Mom's Friend 2","runtime":92,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"An art student named Gwang-ho gets dumped by his girlfriend because she was only his source of comfort, and that he's a Mama's boy and a premature ejaculator. He tries to avoid seeing her by going to a different academy and that's when his mother introduces him to her friend Soo-yeon, a sophisticated and intelligent looking woman. Gwang-ho falls for her.  Gwang-ho's mother suddenly leaves for Australia because his father is sick and Gwang-ho gets to stay in Soo-yeon's house for a few days. Looking at her, he thinks of all the things he would like to do with her and Soo-yeon's niece Ha-kyeong stimulates him to do something about his feelings."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"妈妈的朋友2","runtime":92,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"　　“进来吧~这是你第一次来，不是吗？” 一个叫光昊的艺术系学生被他的女朋友甩了，因为她是他唯一的安慰来源，而且他是妈妈的孩子和早泄者。他试图通过去不同的学校来避免见到她，这时他的母亲把他介绍给她的朋友苏妍，一个成熟而聪明的女人。光昊爱上了她。 光昊的母亲突然动身去澳大利亚，因为他父亲病了，光昊要在秀妍家住几天。看着她，他想到了所有他想和她做的事情，淑妍的侄女哈京昂鼓励他做一些关于自己感情的事情。 有一天，光昊发现在秀妍手机背景中的男子是他的父亲，在秀妍的工作室里发现了一张他父亲与夏京发生性关系的照片。他问秀妍和他父亲的关系。秀妍试图掩饰自己对他的迷恋，但最后她告诉了他真相。光昊收拾行囊，发誓要把这件事告诉母亲，但淑妍求他不要这样做，她会为他做任何事。所以，他请她帮助他成为一个男人，变得擅长性……"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"“어서 와~ 우리집은 처음이지?”  미대 입시학원에 다니는 재수생 광호는 그나마 위안이 되어준 여자친구 미란에게 마마보이에 조루라는 이유로 차이고 만다. 미란을 피해 다른 학원으로 가려는 광호에게 엄마는 미술을 하는 엄마친구 수연을 소개해주고, 광호는 아직 미혼인데다 세련되고 지적인 외모의 수연에게 한눈에 반한다.  때마침 해외출장 중인 아빠가 병이 나서 광호의 엄마가 호주로 가게 되고, 광호는 며칠간 수연의 집에 머무르게 된다. 수연의 집에 온 광호는 수연을 보며 온갖 상상을 하고, 개방적인 성격의 수연의 조카 하경의 도발로 광호의 두근거리는 생활이 시작된다.  어느 날, 광호는 수연의 핸드폰 배경화면에 있는 남자가 자신의 아빠란 사실을 알게 되고, 수연의 작업실에서 하경과 섹스를 하던 중 자신의 아빠를 그린 그림을 보게 된다. 수연에게 아빠와의 관계를 따져 묻는 광호. 당황한 수연은 실은 자신이 혼자 짝사랑 한 거라며 감추고 있던 비밀을 말한다. 엄마에게 이 사실을 알려줘야 한다며 짐을 싸는 광호에게 수연은 어떤 부탁이든 들어줄 테니 비밀을 지켜달라는 간청을 한다. 수연의 간청에 망설이던 광호는 수연에게 섹스에 자신감이 없는 자신을 진짜 남자로 만들어 달라고 제안하는데…"},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"媽媽的朋友2","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"“歡迎光臨~你是第一次來我家嗎？”  藝術類高考复讀生光浩被一直安慰他的女友美蘭趕出校門，因為他是媽媽型男孩且有早洩。試圖避開美蘭並前往另一所學院的光浩被介紹給她母親的美術朋友秀妍。  恰逢其時，光浩的母親因父親在國外出差生病而去了澳大利亞，光浩在秀妍家住了幾天。光浩來到素妍家，看到素妍，思緒萬千，在素妍性格豁達的侄子河景的挑釁下，光浩開始了精彩的生活。  一天，光浩發現秀妍手機背景中的男人是她的父親。光浩向秀妍詢問她與父親的關係。尷尬的秀妍告訴她她隱藏的秘密，聲稱她實際上暗戀自己。光浩收拾行李，說他必須把這件事告訴他媽媽，秀妍懇求他保守秘密，說他會為他做任何事。光浩對秀妍的要求猶豫不決，建議他讓自己成為一個對性沒有信心的真正男人……"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Een kunststudent genaamd Gwang-ho wordt gedumpt door zijn vriendin omdat zij slechts zijn bron van troost was, en omdat hij een moederskindje is en een voortijdige ejaculator. Hij probeert te voorkomen dat hij haar ziet door naar een andere academie te gaan en dan stelt zijn moeder hem voor aan haar vriendin Soo-yeon, een verfijnde en intelligent ogende vrouw. Gwang-ho valt voor haar. Gwang-ho's moeder vertrekt plotseling naar Australië omdat zijn vader ziek is en Gwang-ho een paar dagen in het huis van Soo-yeon mag logeren. Terwijl hij naar haar kijkt, denkt hij aan alle dingen die hij met haar zou willen doen en Soo-yeons nichtje Ha-kyeong stimuleert hem om iets aan zijn gevoelens te doen."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"媽媽的朋友 2","runtime":92,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"“歡迎光臨~你是第一次來我家嗎？” 藝術類高考復讀生光浩被一直安慰他的女友美蘭趕出校門，因為他是媽媽型男孩且有早洩。試圖避開美蘭並前往另一所學院的光浩被介紹給她母親的美術朋友秀妍。 恰逢其時，光浩的母親因父親在國外出差生病而去了澳大利亞，光浩在秀妍家住了幾天。光浩來到素妍家，看到素妍，思緒萬千，在素妍性格豁達的侄子河景的挑釁下，光浩開始了精彩的生活。 一天，光浩發現秀妍手機背景中的男人是她的父親。光浩向秀妍詢問她與父親的關係。尷尬的秀妍告訴她她隱藏的秘密，聲稱她實際上暗戀自己。光浩收拾行李，説他必須把這件事告訴他媽媽，秀妍懇求他保守秘密，説他會為他做任何事。光浩對秀妍的要求猶豫不決，建議他讓自己成為一個對性沒有信心的真正男人……"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"}],"reviews_tmdb":[],"recommendations":[{"id":1112426,"adult":false,"title":"Stree 2","video":false,"overview":"Following the events of 'Stree', the town of Chanderi is being haunted again. This time, women are mysteriously abducted by a terrifying headless entity. Once again, it's up to Vicky and friends to save their town and loved ones.","genre_ids":[27,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.1422,"vote_count":85,"poster_path":"/2NC7sj8rheKxWqLYAbHnCa4mYBH.jpg","release_date":"2024-08-15","vote_average":6.6,"backdrop_path":"/fVV0A67kDjTTQ4CvUn8LoletRmI.jpg","original_title":"स्त्री 2: सरकटे का आतंक","original_language":"hi"},{"id":534171,"adult":false,"title":"Purpose of Reunion 2","video":false,"overview":"I am a teacher! And you are a student! During school days, the first girl Daebeom fell in love with was a practice teacher. He hit on her daringly but she did nothing but treat him like a child. Grown up Daebeom always wants to see her again and one day he heard news that she will attend this alumni reunion. Daebeom decides to seduce her at the reunion. I should sleep with her!","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.2506,"vote_count":16,"poster_path":"/vJjTRTDxCgFFZ7TEkJk36lsc9G4.jpg","release_date":"2017-08-31","vote_average":5.3,"backdrop_path":"/xdFi3dVbWiCvPVAQJMKwY9OnNeg.jpg","original_title":"동창회의 목적 2","original_language":"ko"},{"id":9393,"adult":false,"title":"Before the Fall","video":false,"overview":"In 1942, Friedrich Weimer's boxing skills get him an appointment to a National Political Academy (NaPolA) – high schools that produce Nazi elite. Over his father's objections, Friedrich enrolls. During his year in seventh column, Friedrich encounters hazing, cruelty, death, and the Nazi code. His friendship with Albrecht, the ascetic son of the area's governor, is central to this education.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.7191,"vote_count":355,"poster_path":"/dhTTscZkiQefuq6OeYp9rnvhCBW.jpg","release_date":"2004-07-04","vote_average":7.024,"backdrop_path":"/7Or5uj52hqOnHWDna13OagcX9aP.jpg","original_title":"Napola - Elite für den Führer","original_language":"de"},{"id":1149920,"adult":false,"title":"Too Old for Fairy Tales 2","video":false,"overview":"Your favourite gamer trio is back! This time, Waldek, Staszek and Delfina will spend an adventure-packed summer in the Tatra Mountains. During the trip, Waldek accidentally finds out that his father – the man he has heard so much about from his mum, the person who abandoned his family a long time ago – lives nearby. The boy is determined to find him and ask him about the reasons for his decision. Together with Staszek, under the cover of night, they set out on their mission. The hazards of the mountain trail, however, are nothing compared to what Delfina will have to do. The creative teenager has to hide the truth about the boys’ disappearance from her aunt, the mother of Waldek and… her new partner. How will this secret mission affect the lives of all the characters?  Will Waldek find an answer to the questions that haunt him and understand the actions of his father?","genre_ids":[10751,35,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4225,"vote_count":43,"poster_path":"/lSwdb0yuSVpL7vT8516eHwm4lLJ.jpg","release_date":"2024-03-15","vote_average":6.581,"backdrop_path":"/aXvPIT3m1kyfRr1rvY02bWEyDHl.jpg","original_title":"Za duży na bajki 2","original_language":"pl"},{"id":458355,"adult":false,"title":"Bedroom Eyes","video":false,"overview":"As police investigate a series of murders, all signs point to the lead detective's girlfriend: a gorgeous webcam girl who goes by the name \"Bedroom Eyes.\"","genre_ids":[53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.0794,"vote_count":18,"poster_path":"/uDsQfo4jqRV0yC8K64MNCdetmte.jpg","release_date":"2017-04-04","vote_average":4.167,"backdrop_path":"/t5jq9SJzmNazGwypBo3n0dE9MKJ.jpg","original_title":"Bedroom Eyes","original_language":"en"},{"id":700199,"adult":false,"title":"Mom's Friend 4","video":false,"overview":"Min Jung's husband has been traveling for 300 days and she feels lonely. When her friend Chung Hee moves in next door, Min Jung often visits her house, during which she keeps meeting Jae Ho, Jung Hee's son. After having an impulsive affair with Jae Ho, Min Jung tries to forget about it, saying, \"It was a mistake,\" but she keeps remembering his young body.","genre_ids":[10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.2471,"vote_count":6,"poster_path":"/szssOJ10ZixWA5gZrfYhdKOI0SZ.jpg","release_date":"2018-01-08","vote_average":5.8,"backdrop_path":"/x8jPq4FiXN9Ub0nxilyFVp4OdPL.jpg","original_title":"엄마친구 4","original_language":"ko"},{"id":872585,"adult":false,"title":"Oppenheimer","video":false,"overview":"The story of J. Robert Oppenheimer's role in the development of the atomic bomb during World War II.","genre_ids":[18,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":22.369,"vote_count":11376,"poster_path":"/8Gxv8gSFCU0XGDykEGv7zR1n2ua.jpg","release_date":"2023-07-19","vote_average":8.034,"backdrop_path":"/ycnO0cjsAROSGJKuMODgRtWsHQw.jpg","original_title":"Oppenheimer","original_language":"en"},{"id":693134,"adult":false,"title":"Dune: Part Two","video":false,"overview":"Follow the mythic journey of Paul Atreides as he unites with Chani and the Fremen while on a path of revenge against the conspirators who destroyed his family. Facing a choice between the love of his life and the fate of the known universe, Paul endeavors to prevent a terrible future only he can foresee.","genre_ids":[878,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":22.631,"vote_count":7540,"poster_path":"/1pdfLvkbY9ohJlCjQH2CZjjYVvJ.jpg","release_date":"2024-02-27","vote_average":8.13,"backdrop_path":"/ylkdrn23p3gQcHx7ukIfuy2CkTE.jpg","original_title":"Dune: Part Two","original_language":"en"},{"id":238,"adult":false,"title":"The Godfather","video":false,"overview":"Spanning the years 1945 to 1955, a chronicle of the fictional Italian-American Corleone crime fami