wner notices how naive they are and tells them they have to go for second rounds if they want to make big money. Meanwhile, the ace host girl, Yoon-jeong, comes back after a hiatus due to being sick. These girls begin an ego battle for getting the most customers.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":0.7248,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/5VjzM7qsrNYzKJ456oouDUM0c6R.jpg","release_date":"2019-07-05","vote_average":5,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"룸싸롱 여대생들 2","original_language":"ko"},{"id":857424,"adult":false,"title":"Basketball Triangle","video":false,"overview":"A certain university basketball club. It's a circle of pick-up guys who do blind dates all the time using basketball as a base. Then a gay old man who is a former member of the Japanese national team comes to coach. All of the students are unmotivated, so he tries to teach them the joy of sports, but he is drawn in by the fact that there are so many good-looking guys, and he starts teaching them the joys of homosexuality...","genre_ids":[10749],"popularity":0.1821,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/92U2T8vtLxbEg8LOsrWRrSTKi83.jpg","release_date":"2001-12-28","vote_average":2,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"バスケットボール・トライアングル","original_language":"ja"},{"id":1257576,"adult":false,"title":"Wakamono kari","video":false,"overview":"A gay version of the \"Widow's Boarding House\" series, starring Shinji Kubo as the owner of the boarding house. A straight college student who also has a girlfriend then moves in...","genre_ids":[10749,18,27],"popularity":0.2598,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/jGQL5Y6apqXHeMiJWaQ5Aj3hJJH.jpg","release_date":"1988-09-01","vote_average":2,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"若者狩り","original_language":"ja"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt11772768","twitter_id":null,"facebook_id":null,"wikidata_id":"Q28699303","instagram_id":null},"social_ids":{"twitter":null,"facebook":null,"instagram":null},"gdvg_id":103841,"wiki_plot":null,"wiki_synopsis":null,"wiki_episode_guide":null,"wiki_